'Launch your Personal Brand ' was the theme talk for the third edition of Women, Words and Wine. The event held at the Jacaranda Hotel, Westlands featured wine tasting and cocktails as well as the opportunity to network and enjoy entertainment. Soon after guest speaker Susan Wakhungu-Githuku, Human Performance Dynamics Africa director led 'The Word' segment. Diana Opoti, founder of fashion consultancy Diana Opoti PR took a seat besides Citizen Tv's Kanze Dena for The Couch Conversation. Kenafric deputy general manager marketing Kanana Ndegwa, World Agroforestry Centre executive manager Elizabeth Kariuki, Bamburi Cement director Susan Maingi and General Electric Learning and Development Leader Dr Catherine Munene were some of the leaders present.